<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ذكر ذَلِك فِي كِتَابه <span class="c1">" تَلْخِيص الْمُتَشَابه "</span> وَأطَال فِي بَيَانه -.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٦٩٦)</span> وَمِنْهَا حَدِيث: <span class="c1">" من مَاتَ مَرِيضا مَاتَ شَهِيدا "</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>